run with [upwelling](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=upwelling) and [seedborn muse](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=seedborn muse) and it'll trigger twice and you can use [mind over matter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mind over matter) to untap your lands with your creatures. then hit a [genesis wave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=genesis wave) or something equally as ridiculous.   

